    "In general, the simulator follows a similar hierarchical structure as in ref.",
    "235 by implementing computing in memory (CIM) tiles.",
    "These tiles are composed of a memristive memory crossbar, analogue/digital converters, digital input modulators and sample and hold stages.",
    "Furthermore, each tile has a dedicated controller orchestrating the components responsible for driving the computation.",
